OL,6,FA heart surgeon who sexually assaulted
OL,7,Ffive female staff members working on
OL,8,Fhis department has been described as
OL,9,F"arrogant and crude".
OL,11,FAmal Bose, 55, from Lancaster,
OL,12,Fmolested a number of his female staff
OL,13,Fmembers while in position as a senior
OL,14,Fconsultant and head of the
OL,15,Fcardiovascular unit at Blackpool
OL,16,FVictoria Hospital.
OL,18,FThe victims described "a culture of
OL,19,Finappropriate behaviour that went
OL,20,Funchallenged" due to Bose's seniority
OL,21,Fin the department.
