OL,6,FProsecutor Huw Edwards told a hearing
OL,7,Fat Preston Crown Court that staff
OL,8,Fmembers described Bose's behaviour as
OL,9,Fbeing 'beyond workplace jokes'. He
OL,10,Fsaid "It was sexual targeting of
OL,11,Ffemales - and mainly younger females".
OL,13,FBose was convicted of 12 counts of
OL,14,Fsexual assault relating to five female
OL,15,Fmembers of staff at the hospital
OL,16,Fbetween 2017 and 2019.
