OL,6,FOne victim told the court she was
OL,7,Fgroped by the surgeon as she scrubbed
OL,8,Fin for surgery, while another time he
OL,9,Frested his head on her shoulder,
OL,10,Fmaking her worried what her colleagues
OL,11,Fwould think about the nature of their
OL,12,Frelationship.
OL,14,FEdwards said one woman said Bose
OL,15,Fpulled down her top to expose her
OL,16,Fchest and bra, while another said he
OL,17,Fgroped her breast as he took a pen
OL,18,Ffrom her pocket, and he would often
OL,19,Fstand too close to her and call her
OL,20,F"fresh meat" amongst other
OL,21,Finappropriate comments.
