OL,10,FAnother victim said Bose's behaviour
OL,11,Fwas "a well-known fact", and new
OL,12,Femployees were warned about him.
OL,14,FShe said Bose touched her
OL,15,Finappropriately "every time she saw
OL,16,Fhim", causing her to "develop a
OL,17,Fterrible sickness record" as she
OL,18,Faltered her working pattern to try and
OL,19,Favoid him.
