OL,6,FSenior Crown Prosecutor Sacha Coyne
OL,7,Fsaid: "Amal Bose was in a trusted
OL,8,Fposition at the hospital. He abused
OL,9,Fthis by creating a toxic environment,
OL,10,Fmaking sexual comments, and sexually
OL,11,Fassaulting five women who worked at
OL,12,Fthe hospital.
OL,14,F"He appeared not to recognise the
OL,15,Fserious and lasting impact his actions
OL,16,Fwould have, describing his behaviour
OL,17,Fat trial as "workplace banter".
